
./Relax.Bat
./Cation1.Bat
./Cation2.Bat
./Cation3.Bat
./Pulse.Bat

./gnu.abs.par

./Flux.Bat 1000
./gnu.xsec.par
./gnu.proj.xsec

    or

./Pulse.Perp.Bat
./gnu.abs.perp
etc.

You can execute the gnu scripts while the Pulse step is running, as long as 
it has reached T=100 atomic units.  It goes until 2000 atomic units (40fs).

You can execute the flux step while the Pulse step is running, as long as you
specify a final time less than the current final time.


